        "summary": "XRP is trending as market participants closely monitor the potential passage of the Clarity Act and its expected impact on regulatory status and institutional adoption. While community sentiment remains polarized between long-term bullish holders betting on utility-driven growth and skeptics frustrated by stagnant price action and previous missed targets, active discussions are focused on the token's decoupling from broader market trends and its pivotal role in future cross-border settlement.",
